":2},"title":"Talq on Taqwa: Godfearing righteousness is to obey Allah by His light","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 27, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Bakr ibn Abdullah reported: Talq ibn Habib, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cGodfearing righteousness is to act in obedience to Allah upon a light from Allah, hoping in the mercy of Allah. Godfearing righteousness is to abandon disobedience to Allah upon a light from Allah, fearing the punishment\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7503,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/03\/disobedience-to-mothers\/","url_meta":{"origin":38037,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Parents: Allah forbids disobedience to mothers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Mughirah ibn Sha\u2019bah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah has forbidden you from disobeying your mothers, withholding charity, demanding from others, and burying your daughters alive. Allah disapproves that you spread talebearing and gossip, ask many unnecessary questions, and waste your wealth.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38042,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/07\/29\/true-wealth-not-outward\/","url_meta":{"origin":38037,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hearts: True wealth is not outward, rather in t